        "public": true,
        "initialMessages": "👋 I'm the **Check Point Threat Prevention** AI agent — I manage your Threat Prevention policy: profiles, IPS protections, exceptions and indicators.\n\n**Try one of these:**\n• List the Threat Prevention profiles\n• Which profile is strictest and what does it activate?\n• Search IPS protections related to log4j",
